1
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,200
Every spring

2
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:46,530
when all the peach blossoms bloom here

3
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:48,410
it's an endless sea of flowers.

4
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,490
The peach trees here

5
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:53,000
are indeed different from those in the city,

6
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,130
they're beautiful.

7
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,360
Haozi said you should paint the local scenery,

8
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,690
so I should be a good host

9
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,320
and take you around to explore,

10
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:01,580
to find inspiration for your paintings.

11
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,920
Actually,

12
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,620
I watch your video channel every day,

13
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:08,039
and I've already found a lot of inspiration from it.

14
00:01:08,039 --> 00:01:08,570
So are you

15
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,720
making good progress with your painting?

16
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:11,650
It's going well.

17
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,760
Here I feel

18
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,760
as if

19
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:16,840
my mother in heaven

20
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:18,500
is silently watching over me,

21
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,420
so I can quickly get into the zone,

22
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:22,440
and paint whatever I want.

23
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,130
This tree is called Nilan Wood.

24
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,280
This tree has a name?

25
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,600
I named it myself.

26
00:01:32,479 --> 00:01:33,800
Nilan in Tibetan

27
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,840
means 'dream'.

28
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:36,680
Once when I was little,

29
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,080
I came out alone to herd cattle

30
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,479
and got lost around here.

31
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:42,120
I slept under this tree all night.

32
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,320
In my dream, a goddess told me

33
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:46,039
she was the deity who guards peach trees

34
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,160
and would protect me.

35
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:47,840
Until the next day,

36
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,770
when my family found me, I realized

37
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,600
there had been wild animals prowling around that night,

38
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:53,000
they had killed two cows,

39
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,420
and I had no idea at all.

40
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,440
But

41
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:00,200
all these trees look the same.

42
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:02,250
How did you recognize this one?

43
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,080
I can distinguish

44
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:06,640
the differences between every peach tree here.

45
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,120
Every flower,

46
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:10,000
every blade of grass, every tree

47
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,130
in this world is unique.

48
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:14,970
There are no two identical trees in the world.

49
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:16,840
It's called

50
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,160
Nilan Wood.

51
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:18,640
Hmm.

52
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,400
Actually,

53
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,810
I often have a recurring dream.

54
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,160
In the dream,

55
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:30,120
I see my mother standing in front of a peach blossom tree,

56
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,079
smiling at me.

57
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,079
Just like that drawing in your sketchbook.

58
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,040
This is the only photo

59
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,480
my mother left me.

60
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:41,000
I've already asked around for you,

61
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,280
but there are too many people named Ciyang,

62
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,280
without any other specific information,

63
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,000
it's indeed difficult to find her.

64
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:47,880
It's okay,

65
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,120
it must be difficult to find her,

66
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,050
after all, it's been over 20 years.

67
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,079
Look,

68
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,060
that's Namcha Barwa Peak.

69
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,160
Today

70
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,960
