71
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,660
I can't see it anymore.

72
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,320
It's okay,

73
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,450
even if you can't see it,

74
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:19,240
the mountain is still there.

75
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:32,800
Everyone.

76
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:33,800
Everyone.

77
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,720
You guys

78
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,200
are going viral.

79
