95
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,720
Yes, absolutely.

96
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,160
Every guest gets one.

97
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,320
I've already replied to users from our official account.

98
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,519
We'll give portraits to all our guests.

99
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,570
Haozi, you're awesome!

100
