106
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,680
Get ready to take orders.

107
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,340
How's it going?

108
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,440
It's true,

109
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,800
we're fully booked for the weekend.

110
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,240
See that?

111
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:38,800
Hurry up,

112
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,159
tell Baima to find someone to help.

113
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,040
Qianqian,

114
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,280
