245
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,160
Once I've figured it out,

246
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:19,760
Ding Nian,

247
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,170
you'll get your fair share.

248
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,240
Thanks, sis.

249
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,480
About the cultural products,

250
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,140
I've ordered some notebooks,

251
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,620
postcards and stamps.

252
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,240
When they're ready,

253
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,640
I'll put some in your inn,

254
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,440
and some at the post office,

255
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,570
to see how they sell.

256
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,880
Here's the contract.

257
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,560
Since I'm using your artwork,

258
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:42,880
let's keep this professional,

259
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,160
and pay the proper royalties.

260
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,800
We'll go with

261
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,760
an advance plus commission

262
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:46,760
for your payment.

263
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,040
Is this for real?

264
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,200
I feel like I'm dreaming.

265
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:52,240
No rush, take your time to review it.

266
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,560
Contact me anytime if you have questions.

267
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,560
I'll be going now.

268
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,480
Thanks, Hao.

269
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,410
Bye, no problem.

270
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:02,800
I really didn't expect this.

271
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,130
It all happened so fast,

272
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,680
