275
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:14,080
Thank me?

276
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,640
That tree,

277
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,360
the Nilan tree,

278
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:21,500
